UE5 Blueprint File - ABP_NPC_Shared_v01
=======================================

This is a Blueprint Animation Instance that extends UAnimInstance (C++ class).

To create this blueprint in Unreal Engine 5.2+:
1. Right-click in Content Browser
2. Search for "AnimInstance"
3. Select "ABP_NPC_Shared_v01"
4. Click "Create"

Components:
- IdleMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- WalkMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- RunMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- GestureMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- EmotionMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- DangerMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- WorkMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- SchoolMontages (Array of AnimMontage)
- BlendSpace_Gait (BlendSpace)
- BlendSpace_Expression (BlendSpace)
- BlendSpace_Speed (BlendSpace)

Variables:
- WalkSpeed (Float)
- RunSpeed (Float)
- Happiness (Float)
- Sadness (Float)
- Anger (Float)
- Speed (Float)
- CurrentState (Enum: Idle, Walking, Working, Sleeping, Dialogue, Combat, Fleeing, Questing)

Functions:
- PlayIdleAnimation()
- PlayWalkAnimation()
- PlayRunAnimation()
- PlayGestureAnimation(FString)
- PlayEmotionAnimation(FString)
- PlayDangerAnimation(FString)
- PlayWorkAnimation(FString)
- PlaySchoolAnimation(FString)
- UpdateBlendSpaceGait(float, float)
- UpdateBlendSpaceExpression(float, float, float)
- UpdateBlendSpaceSpeed(float)

Note: This blueprint must be compiled after adding components.
Note: This blueprint requires animation assets from animators.
Note: This blueprint requires blend spaces from animators.
Note: This blueprint requires animation slots from animators.